{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 4 shows that the LID and LRC results are consistent.",
    "The graphs were produced using a subset of 1M points randomly sampled from each dataset, and 𝑘 = 100.",
    "Note that the orange horizontal lines in Figures 4a and 4b Queries.",
    "Query sets include 100 vectors processed sequentially, not in batches, mimicking a realworld scenario where queries are unpredictable [58,59,109].",
    "Results with 1 million queries are extrapolated from 100 query sets."
  ]
}